# ── Build artifacts (build from source with `make`) ──
# NOTE: don't ignore a root "Vineport" — the FS is case-insensitive, so it would
# also ignore the `vineport` CLI. The app binary lives in Vineport.app/ (below).
steamwebhelper_wrapper.exe
/Vineport.app/
/dist/
*.dylib

